TopicTitle: KSP Youtube channel (3-7 videos a week!)

Articles.Content:
Hello there, this monday I started a YT channel for kerbal space program, I'm from sweden but the videos are in English but since I'm swedish my English Isn't the best, if you want you can check it out and I promise at least 3 videos a week (KSP) up to 7 of them, when I reaches some subscribers I'll also start doing 12 and 24 H livestreams (KSP)

Please check out and if you want please subscribe...

This first week I have a kickstarter week where I upload one video a day
